title: SA joins Africa’s free trade area but why is Nigeria hesitant?
description:
SA has joined the African Continental Free Trade Agreement and also why Nigeria is delaying? And Rob Davies discusses the impact of global trade tariffs spats on the South African economy. CNBC Africa is joined by Adrian Saville, Professor of Economics, Finance and Strategy at GIBS.
